title: Daft.Punk.Live.at.Choachella[2006].DivX
description:
I take no credit for this video, it was onbefore the site went down and I was lucky enough to have downloaded the full DivX quality version.

This is a Daft Punk show in April 2006 and was taped by 3 people standing in different parts of the crowd. The videos were merged together and the audio taken from the soundboard was put over them. This is one of the best fan made concert videos I have ever seen.
